description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 11, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 33, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Nine Lives for East, 2 for South, and 2 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70113-99224-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [33 Votes, Common]
